I understand you're trying to minimize changes but I think the code would be slightly clearer/better if we avoid the redundant assignment, i.e.
if (record.getPartitionKey().isPresent()) {
    keyValue = record.getPartitionKey().get().getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8);
}

